description: All of Milwaukee, old and young, love the succulently soulful cuisine from Bungalow on Wheels. An extension of the beloved Bungalow Restaurant, this truck can satisfy your appetite, curbside. You’ll find all your comfort food favorites: Smothered Chicken, Fried Catfish, Liver & Onions, Cornbread, Sweet Potato Pie, Mac & Cheese, and more... and it’s all so dang yummy!Next time you need a “whoa”-worthy meal, Bungalow on Wheels is the way to go.
name: Bungalow on Wheels
